---
---

<section id="features" class="features-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Built for Scale, Designed for Results</h2>
      <p>Enterprise-grade features that automate your entire content pipeline</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🧠</div>
        <h3>Context-Aware Intelligence</h3>
        <p>Robots analyze your website's existing content to avoid duplicates and maintain topical consistency</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔗</div>
        <h3>Automatic Internal Linking</h3>
        <p>SEO Robot creates topical authority through intelligent internal link recommendations</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
        <h3>Data Visualization</h3>
        <p>Generate interactive charts, tables, and topic mesh visualizations from research data</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
        <h3>Competitor Analysis</h3>
        <p>Article Robot scrapes competitor sites with Firecrawl to identify content gaps and opportunities</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">✅</div>
        <h3>Pydantic Validation</h3>
        <p>Strict schema validation ensures data quality and consistency across all robot outputs</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>Blacksmith CI/CD</h3>
        <p>2x faster builds with 75% cost reduction. 3,000 free minutes monthly for rapid deployment</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔍</div>
        <h3>Exa AI Search</h3>
        <p>Neural search and content extraction powers Newsletter Robot's intelligent curation</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📈</div>
        <h3>Quality Metrics</h3>
        <p>Track relevance scores, uniqueness, generation time, and SEO compliance in real-time</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🚀</div>
        <h3>Schema.org Markup</h3>
        <p>Automatic structured data generation for enhanced search engine visibility</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: var(--color-light-gray);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    background: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
